br.com.jbugbrasil.bot.api.conf.systemproperties

Annotation Type BotProperty


  • @Qualifier
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={FIELD,METHOD})
public @interface BotProperty
    Qualificador para injetar System Properties pertinentes ao Bot Exemplo: 
      @BotProperty(name = "br.com.jbugbrasil.myproperty", required = true)
  Object myProperty;
